\cos\left(\alpha\right) & \sin\left(\alpha\right) & 0 & 0\\
0 & 0 & 0 & 1
\end{array}\right)\left(\begin{array}{c}
x_{e}\\
y_{e}\\
z_{e}\\
w_{e}
\end{array}\right)=\left(\begin{array}{c}
